.close_icon
	%span{:aria => {hidden: 'true'}, :class => 'icon-DBPS-Dev-Assets-SRG-07'}

.content
	-#.modal_steps
		%a.step.one{:href => '#'}
			%span.icon.icon-closedone
		%a.step.two{:href => '#'}
			%span.icon.icon-opentwo
		%a.step.three{:href => '#'}
			%span.icon.icon-openthree
	%h2
		Hello! ¡Hola! Olá! Xin chào!
		%br/
		%br/
		Does your child have specialized language needs?
		%br/
		If yes, please check the student's native language below.

	= form_tag student_ell_preferences_path, method: :post, remote: true, 'data-type' => 'script' do

		%p
			= radio_button_tag '[student]ell_language', 'Cape Verdean', current_student.ell_language == 'Cape Verdean'
			Cape Verdean
		%p
			= radio_button_tag '[student]ell_language', 'Chinese', current_student.ell_language == 'Chinese'
			Chinese
		%p
			= radio_button_tag '[student]ell_language', 'Haitian Creole', current_student.ell_language == 'Haitian Creole'
			Haitian Creole
		%p
			= radio_button_tag '[student]ell_language', 'Spanish', current_student.ell_language == 'Spanish'
			Spanish
		%p
			= radio_button_tag '[student]ell_language', 'Vietnamese', current_student.ell_language == 'Vietnamese'
			Vietnamese
		%p
			= radio_button_tag '[student]ell_language', 'Other', current_student.ell_language == 'Other'
			Other (including multi-lingual)
		%p
			= radio_button_tag '[student]ell_language', '', current_student.ell_language.present? ? false : true
			Not Applicable

		.btn
			= submit_tag 'Next', disable_with: 'Working...', id: 'ell_next_button', class: 'orange_submit'

	.footnote.light
		%p{style: "color: #565656;"}
			As part of the registration process, every applicant is asked to complete a Home Language Survey.
			The results of this Survey determine whether a child needs additional language assessment at our Newcomers Assessment and Counseling Center.
			If this is the case, a child's school choices may expand beyond his/her Home Based options to include program seats in a wider community cluster of schools.
			The ELL tab on your results page will show you which schools may be available to child, pending his/her test results.
			For more information on clusters, the Language Assessment, or the Newcomer's Assessment and Counseling Center, please call a Welcome Center near you or contact the Newcomers Center directly at: 617-635-1565

:javascript
	$('#ell_next_button').click(function() {
		$('#ell_next_button').prop('value', 'Working...');
	});
	$(".close_icon").click(function() {
		$(".dialog_box").fadeOut("fast").removeClass("active");
	});
	$(".dialog_box").click(function(e){
		e.stopPropagation();
	});
